{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Incorruptible Sitre |image = XC3 Incorruptible Sitre.png |caption = Incorruptible Sitre |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Keves Forces]] |level = 68 |area = [[Keves Castle]] ([[Ascension Hall (XC3)|Ascension Hall]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Fate]]'' |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = |gold = |hp = |strength = |ether = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate = }} '''Incorruptible Sitre''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] who is part of the [[Keves Forces]] and is fought at level 68 in [[Keves Castle]] during ''[[Fate]]''.
== Story == She is one of the Four Divine Wings staging an armed uprising within the castle, alongside [[Mediator Adrinael]], [[Overfist Balroy]], and [[Puckish Lycconen]]. She was tortured by [[Hexen]] in the past, and has trauma as a result from it. {{clr}}
